responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "7ACC42244D08FC09727A3D8EA742B74B", "Hecatomb is the divine master of hexes. His curses litter this world and others. Among those curses are the relics of depravity that were once contained within the vaults were I the Antiquitor acted as caretaker, one and many. In a futile attempt of redemption, we now scour this realm to seize the cursed curios before the Divine Carnage claims them for Duzahk. ")
